<hr />

>>> a = 21

>>> b = 10

=== Igualidad ===

>>> ( a == b )<br />
False

=== Inigualidad ===
>>> ( a != b )<br />
True

=== Inigualidad en Python 2.x pero NO en 3.x ===

>>> ( a <> b )<br />
  File "<stdin>", line 1
    ( a <> b )
         ^
 SyntaxError: invalid syntax

=== Menor que ===

>>> ( a < b )<br />
False

=== Mayor que ===

>>> ( a > b )<br />
True

=== Menor que o igual ===

>>> (a <= b)<br />
False

>>> b <= a<br />
True

=== Mayor que o igual ===

>>> (a >= b)<br />
True

>>> b >= a<br />
False



